Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:03.17,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,"所有注视着你的..."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.83,0:00:06.06,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,"...都是幻觉..."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.94,0:00:13.01,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,从我躺在地上的角度,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.01,0:00:16.04,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,我无法看清她低垂的面容。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.02,0:00:25.79,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,在这阵淡淡的雨幕之后,你的面容又将现出何等模样...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.85,0:00:28.19,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,"我将了结你的苦痛..."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.56,0:00:31.56,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,天使吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.53,0:00:38.50,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,那闪耀舞动的光羽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.46,0:00:38.50,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,是在祝福着我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:38.50,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,还是说...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.93,0:00:44.97,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,啊...原来如此,我终于明白了。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.01,0:00:49.98,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,她要用那把剑杀了我...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.11,0:00:57.25,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,少女缓缓跪在我躺卧的身前。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.22,0:01:01.62,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,她仍旧低垂着头颅,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:04.86,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,轻轻地将我的手握在掌心。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.86,0:01:12.20,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,我把身体交托给她的温柔拥抱;
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.93,0:01:12.20,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,我只庆幸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.03,0:01:12.20,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,她没有注视着我。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.24,0:01:18.61,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,在我耳边,传来低语;
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.77,0:01:21.14,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,夹杂着噪音,美妙而又不协调。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.28,0:01:26.08,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,但是...我听不太清楚。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.38,0:01:38.16,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,温暖...柔软...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.52,0:01:38.16,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,温柔...甘美的触感。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.13,0:01:41.63,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,奇迹般地,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:47.07,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,仿佛是麻醉剂一般,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:47.07,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,我身体的战栗逐渐平息下来。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.10,0:01:53.81,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,她温柔的气息拂过我的脸颊。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:56.38,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,闻起来竟如此甜美...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.38,0:02:01.38,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,突然,我感到胸口一沉。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.42,0:02:04.59,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,那把巨大的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.59,0:02:11.59,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,穿透了我的皮肤...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.22,0:02:11.59,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,钻进了我的血肉...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.16,0:02:11.59,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,缠绕在我的骨骼...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:15.66,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,缓缓没入我体内最深处。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.66,0:02:24.07,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,但是...在她亲吻的麻醉之下,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.40,0:02:24.07,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,我再也感受不到丝毫痛楚。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:27.18,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,我万万想不到会有这样温柔的死法...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:30.28,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,光是想想就撼人心扉,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:32.58,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,让我几乎要落下泪来。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.61,0:02:35.55,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,想要隐藏泪水,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:42.06,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,我抬头望向那灰蒙蒙的天空,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:42.06,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,雨丝仍在缓缓飘落。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.13,0:02:49.53,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,是因为雨水还是泪水,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.86,0:02:49.53,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,那天空变得如此朦胧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.87,0:02:54.97,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,我再也感受不到任何注视了。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:02:58.57,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,我再也感受不到任何事物。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:03:04.91,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,随着意识的消逝,我朝天空伸出手去。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:07.58,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,有谁能告诉我...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:09.62,Chaos;Head dialogues,,0,0,0,,...我们的天空去了哪里...?
